{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act29side_level_act29side_08_end","storyGroup":"act29side","storySort":18,"storyDependence":"act29side_level_act29side_08_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"ZT-8","storyName":"夜歌“未见的高塔”","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"费德里科和阿尔图罗分别与失踪已久的少女尤利娅对话，逐步揭开荒域的神秘面纱。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act29side/level_act29side_08_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act29side_08","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":16,"next":18,"characters":["薇薇安","薇薇安娜","围观的路人A","围观的路人B","费德里科","尤利娅","阿尔图罗","？？？"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":5},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":6},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":7},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1121_1#1$1","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":8},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"我正要出门，要跟我一起吗？","id":9},{"type":"dialog","id":10},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#2$1","id":11},{"type":"delay","time":"0.8","id":12},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#4$1","id":13},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"......好。","id":15},{"type":"dialog","id":16},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":17},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":18},{"type":"charslot","id":19},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":20,"musicid":0},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_animal_loop","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"a","id":21},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.3","channel":"a","fadetime":"2","id":22},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":23},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":24},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":25},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#7$1","id":26},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1121_1#1$1","id":27},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":28},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":29},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1121_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"先等我一下。","id":31},{"type":"text","text":"[charslot(slot = \"r\", name = \"avg_4098_vvana_1#10$1\", focus=\"r\")  ]","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"怎么了？","id":33},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1121_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"三、二、一......","id":35},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1121_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"希曼夫人，下午好！","id":37},{"type":"dialog","id":38},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"3","id":39},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.5","isblock":"true","id":40},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_openwindow","volume":"0.6","id":41},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":42},{"type":"text","text":"临街的窗户应声而开，眉头紧锁的女性拿着画笔悠悠远眺，小女孩立刻踮着脚向她招手，笑容如满街的金盏花一样明媚。","id":43},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#10$1","focus":"n","id":44},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1121_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"希曼夫人每天这个时候都会开窗休息。画了一上午的画，看看远方，听听音乐，养养精神，找找灵感。","id":46},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1121_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"奇怪，希曼夫人看起来心情不太好，都没回应我就把窗户关上了。大概是作画不顺利吧，晚上我应该和妈妈去看看她。","id":48},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"你对附近很熟悉，小薇薇安。","id":50},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1121_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"你说卡尔·施密特街吗？当然啦，我都在这儿过完十岁生日了！","id":52},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"爸爸妈妈一直住在这里？","id":54},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1121_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"短暂地搬出去过几次，我也没太懂原因......但绕了一圈，最后又搬了回来。","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"放在整个崔林特尔梅看，卡尔·施密特街确实很不起眼啦，只有一些花店、酒吧、颜料铺，都是上了年纪的矮楼，连一座高塔都没有。","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"住在这里的都是普通人，还有一些落魄的艺术家和贵族......但爸爸妈妈很喜欢这里。","id":58},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"有人来找过他们的麻烦吗？","id":60},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1121_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"爸爸说，刚开始的时候有过，但他既然决定留下来，就已经做好了万全的准备。","id":62},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"沃尔纳·冯·霍赫贝格想办法让自己变成了一个普通人？","id":64},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1121_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"爸爸也没那么普通哦！虽然他只是在维恩区的平民学校里教文学，但那些哥哥姐姐可尊敬他了。","id":66},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"......嗯。","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"他应该动用了自己在施彤领和崔林特尔梅的所有人脉，花光了全部的积蓄，兴许连长相也换了......","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"割舍自己所拥有的一切，并不容易。","id":70},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"对了，薇薇安，你手上提着的，是蛋糕吗？","id":72},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1121_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"是呀。我跟着邻居姐姐学了好久呢。金盏花的花蕊有一点点苦味，但磨成粉放进蛋糕里，既有香味还能解腻。","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"妈妈刚在巴赫区找到一份工作，工资比之前高一点，而且是在她最爱的诗刊当编辑！就是要很晚才能回家......","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"所以我主动申请给妈妈送一个月的午饭。","id":76},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"会觉得辛苦吗？","id":78},{"type":"dialog","id":79},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_wind","volume":"1","id":80},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1121_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":81},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"唔~你有没有闻到香味？","id":83},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"香味？","id":85},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1121_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"起风的时候，前面那家咖啡店的香气会远远地飘过来。","id":87},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1121_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"我帮着多做一点事情，爸爸妈妈就不会那么累，这样周末的时候就能带我去参加希曼夫人举办的聚会啦。","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"爸爸妈妈会牵着我的手，穿过长长的巷子去希曼夫人家。那里有很多有意思的人，他们弹琴很好听，说话也很好听。","id":90},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1121_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安","text":"薇薇安也很喜欢这里，薇薇安不觉得辛苦。","id":92},{"type":"dialog","id":93},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":94},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"......这样也很好。","id":96},{"type":"dialog","id":97},{"type":"charslot","duration":"0.5","isblock":"true","id":98},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":99},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":100},{"type":"subtitle","text":"薇薇安娜。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":101},{"type":"subtitle","text":"这样的生活，也很好。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":102},{"type":"subtitle","id":103},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":104},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":105},{"type":"charslot","id":106},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/91/Avg_bg_28_g1_gorgeousstreets.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":107},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":108},{"type":"playmusic","volume":"0.6","id":109,"musicid":1},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"a","id":110},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.5","channel":"a","fadetime":"2","id":111},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":112},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":113},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_497_1#1$1","focus":"n","id":114},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_496_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"围观的路人A","text":"怎么回事？刚刚那是......露辛达？","id":116,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_496_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"围观的路人A","text":"一个规规矩矩的平民，能得罪什么人，难道写了什么不该写的诗？治安官来得那么快，有什么说法吗？","id":117,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_496_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_497_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"围观的路人B","text":"来得快，走得也快，还能有什么说法！（低声）别瞎打听了，应该是因为她的丈夫。","id":119,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_497_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_496_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"围观的路人A","text":"沃尔纳？","id":121,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_496_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_497_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"围观的路人B","text":"我也是听说，他居然是施彤领选帝侯的继承人，隐姓埋名，守着妻子和女儿在卡尔·施密特街过了十年平凡日子。","id":123,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_497_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_496_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"围观的路人A","text":"平时还经常和他们一家三口打招呼来着，真没看出来，隐藏得挺好的......","id":125,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_496_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_497_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"围观的路人B","text":"唉，怎么可能瞒得住！","id":127,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_497_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"围观的路人B","text":"据说早上的时候，沃尔纳就没有出现在教室里，甚至不知道带走他的人是霍赫贝格家族的属臣还是女皇之声。","id":128,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_497_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"围观的路人B","text":"十有八九是弗里达·希曼告的密，那女人其实疯得很......","id":129,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7c/Avg_avg_npc_497_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_496_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"围观的路人A","text":"嘘，小点声小点声。","id":131,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_496_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":132},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"2","id":133},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#4$1","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"——！","id":135},{"type":"dialog","id":136},{"type":"charslot","id":137},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cakebgflgrnd","volume":"1","id":138},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":139},{"type":"text","text":"装着蛋糕的袋子摔在了地上，发出沉闷的响声。","id":140},{"type":"text","text":"薇薇安娜听见了抽泣声。那样纤弱的肩膀轻轻颤动，像是在狂风中摇晃的花茎。","id":141},{"type":"text","text":"薇薇安娜紧紧握住了小女孩的手。","id":142},{"type":"dialog","id":143},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1121_1#4$1","duration":"1","id":144},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","posfrom":"-200,0","posto":"-200,0","duration":"0","id":145},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#10$1","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":146},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":147},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4098_vvana_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇薇安娜","text":"薇薇安......不要看。","id":149},{"type":"dialog","id":150},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":151},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":152},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":153},{"type":"charslot","id":154},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":155},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1125_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","duration":"0","id":156},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1127_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","duration":"0","id":157},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":158},{"type":"playmusic","volume":"0.6","id":159,"musicid":2},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_dimnlspamb","volume":"0.2","loop":"true","channel":"d","id":160},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":161},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1125_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"-100,0","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0","duration":"0.5","id":162},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1127_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"-100,0","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0","duration":"0.5","id":163},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":164},{"type":"charslot","id":165},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":166},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","focus":"n","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"尤利娅·许勒尔女士，我只能隐约捕捉到一些光影。你能否为我指明残党出没的位置？","id":168,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"我的守护铳或许能发挥作用。我将保证你的安全。","id":169,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"啊......","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"执行者先生，你应该是误会了。","id":172},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"那些人，并不是来对我做什么的。","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"最开始看见这些戴面具的家伙时，我也会远远地躲起来，但后来发现他们并不在意我的存在。","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"他们在“崔林特尔梅”的某个区域现身，往往说明那里又有敌人来侵扰了......他们更像是一种“信号”。","id":176},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"“敌人”？","id":178,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0e/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"不是真正的敌人，我、我不知道该怎么解释。","id":180},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"就像是......无法理解的自然灾害，反常的坏天气，成真的噩梦......","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"尤其是最近，“崔林特尔梅”的气候变得越来越差。云很沉，晚霞也像是褪色了。还经常有动静大得离奇的雷声......","id":183},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"有好几次一觉醒来，就会发现“崔林特尔梅”又空了一块。","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"那么多显眼的建筑，像是被什么东西硬生生地给抠了去，它们原本的位置只剩下一片空白，就好像历史凭空缺了一部分。","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"敌人了无痕迹地抹去不同时代的高塔，一点点地啃食着“崔林特尔梅”，让它变得残缺。","id":187},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......","id":189,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/37/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"而迟早有一天，会轮到我生活的这小小的巷子。","id":191},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"所以你才会在我使用守护铳时跳出来阻止。","id":193,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"你一直守在这里。","id":194,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"嗯嗯。我之前都没有见过你。","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"这段时间，我一直都有这个预感，很强烈。","id":197},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"预感。","id":199,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"预感通常只是一种心理暗示。没有逻辑支撑，很难切实指导行动。","id":200,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"但巫王残党确实出现了......","id":202,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/37/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"执行者先生，当你在一个地方生活了五年十年，成为它的一部分，你就会像羽兽那样，提前嗅到暴风雨的味道。","id":204},{"type":"dialog","id":205},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","text":"","id":206},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":207},{"type":"charslot","id":208},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","id":209},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#5$1","id":210},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","style":"slider","inverse":"true","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":211},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","focus":"n","id":212},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"您想要，去帮助“赫尔昏佐伦的余音”？","id":214},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"不，这是我自己的事情。如果今天他们没有出现，我也会自己想办法的。","id":216},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"可是，您要如何对抗那些灾害、坏天气和噩梦呢？","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"您随身携带的这些法术装置......？","id":219},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"其实这段时间，我每天都会去不同的地方，尤其是那些建筑消失过的“空白”和“边缘”。","id":221},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"很危险......","id":223},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"但我在那些地方收集到了足够数量的装置。","id":225},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"似乎是某种能够联通法阵、采集信息的法术回声装置。","id":227},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"阿尔图罗小姐，如果那些戴面具的家伙真是“赫尔昏佐伦的余音”，那这些回声装置应该是巫王用来对付敌人的。","id":229},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"它们肯定能派上用场！","id":231},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......您是想，自己改造这条街？","id":233},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"金盏花小巷靠近博登区的外围，非常不起眼。除了那些外地游客、采风的画家和流浪的诗人，其实没多少人愿意特意过来。","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"哪怕整个博登区，放在崔林特尔梅的二十二个城区里，也没多特别。","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"而在这个“崔林特尔梅”，有那么多曾在历史上赫赫有名的神奇高塔......或许不会有人顾得上这样一条普普通通的小巷子。","id":237},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"但它是生我养我的地方......而且没人比我更熟悉它。","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"我知道它什么时候最热闹，什么时候最安静。","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"我熟悉它所有的声音——流浪歌手的演唱、行人随口哼的小调、石板路上杂沓的脚步声、雨水打湿金盏花和布棚的动静......","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"我知道整条街上，哪里埋着的共鸣管线还能运作，哪些拐角的法术雕塑可以替代已经损毁的部分......","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"以及怎样能以最便捷的方式将它们全部串联起来，再用这些回声装置将它们激活！","id":243},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"可您并不清楚，改造后的共鸣管线能起到什么作用。","id":245},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"这些装置遗落在那些建筑消失的空白里，本身便说明......","id":247},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"唔，阿尔图罗小姐，我总得做点什么啊。","id":249},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"而且，我总能做到什么。","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"这是我很小的时候就告诉自己的事情。","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"我跟自己说，要好好照顾扬，也要好好照顾自己。不要像爸爸妈妈那样......","id":253},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"您的父母......","id":255},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"很早就去世了，应该是1077年......","id":257},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"您的父母受到了双子女皇政变的牵连？","id":259},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"不。他们只是再普通不过的普通人。","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"他们当时生着病，远处巫王始源之塔倒塌的巨响，屋子外面士兵来来往往的靴子声......加剧了他们的病情。","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"他们总觉得下一秒就会有宪兵推门进来将我们抓走，甚至将整条街都夷为平地。在动荡的年月，发生什么都不足为奇。","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"他们在巴赫先生开展“光荣首都计划”之前，死在了自己的恐惧里。","id":264},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"当巨大的喧嚣盖过一切时，我们往往只能听见自己内心的声音。那些恐惧、惊忧都被自己放大了。","id":266},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"尤利娅女士，请原谅我说不出更多的话安慰您。","id":268},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"不用不用。我只是想说，我无法允许自己就这样弄丢生活的底气。","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"阿尔图罗小姐，或许你依然看不清周围的景象......我们刚刚从街尾的画廊一路走过来，前面就是我待了快十年的咖啡馆。","id":271},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"最开始去那儿打工，只是为了维持家里的开销。店老板人很好，允许我和扬住在后院闲置的仓库里。","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"我把仓库改造成了房间，还专门给扬隔出了个练习法术的小屋子。","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"这孩子很有天赋，街上有术师用法术修复雕塑，他看了几眼，回家琢磨一晚上，就把自己的房间门变成了“声控”的。","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"我跟洛里斯商量过，等他到了上大学的时候，就送他去路德维格大学学习法术。","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"洛里斯拍着胸脯说会努力在崔林特尔梅做出一番事业，到时候就可以当扬的推荐人。","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"后来这家咖啡馆快倒闭的时候，我用所有的积蓄把它盘了下来。","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"老板是我，服务员也是我。我甚至开始尝试自己调制新咖啡，作为重新开业那天的特别单品......","id":279},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"危险无从预料，但生活是切实的。","id":281},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"您只是想要保护它。","id":283},{"type":"dialog","id":284},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":285},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":286},{"type":"charslot","id":287},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":288},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":289},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":290},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":291},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","posfrom":"200,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"1.5","isblock":"true","id":292},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_mgcdevcstartp","volume":"1","id":293},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":294},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"从街口的钢琴教室到这里，沿路一共八段共鸣管线，这些回声装置恰好能和管线上的接口相嵌合......","id":296},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#5$1","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"我就说它们是有用的！","id":298},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"不难理解。","id":300,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"崔林特尔梅的共鸣管线，本就是巴赫在主持“光荣首都计划”时，针对巫王时期铺设在全城的法术符线进行的调音。","id":301,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#5$1","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"再往前几步，就是我的咖啡馆，这一半的改造工程就算完工了。","id":303},{"type":"dialog","id":304},{"type":"charslot","id":305},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.5","channel":"d","fadetime":"2","id":306},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":307},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1125_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","duration":"0","id":308},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1127_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0.7","duration":"0","id":309},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":310},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1125_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"-100,0","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0","duration":"0.5","id":311},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1127_1#1$1","bstart":"0.9","bend":"1","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"-100,0","afrom":"0.7","ato":"0","duration":"0.5","id":312},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":313},{"type":"charslot","id":314},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"又出现了，对吧？","id":316,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0e/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"嗯。就在咖啡馆对面的拐角。","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"看来我得加快速度了。","id":319},{"type":"dialog","id":320},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"d","fadetime":"1.5","id":321},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":322},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act28side/m_avg_wasteland_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":323,"musicid":3},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#2$1","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"......","id":325},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"怎么了？","id":327,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#2$1","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"有些，熟悉。","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"跟那天的情形，似乎一模一样......","id":330},{"type":"dialog","id":331},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":332},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":333},{"type":"charslot","id":334},{"type":"background","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","screenadapt":"coverall","id":335},{"type":"backgroundtween","xFrom":"130","xTo":"-125","duration":"60","ease":"OutQuad","block":"false","id":336},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":337},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"0.5","fillto":"0.15","fadetime":"2","id":338},{"type":"curtain","direction":"4","fillfrom":"0.5","fillto":"0.15","fadetime":"2","id":339},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"那天是咖啡馆营业的第一天，我站在店门口等洛里斯和扬......他们来得有些慢。","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"其实我知道这俩家伙想趁着“开张大吉”做什么，他们的小动作太明显了。","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"洛里斯还特地跑到其他街区的花店去订花，又叮嘱我一定要站在街上最显眼的位置等他......","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"他都没发现自己前一天来帮忙的时候不小心把订单落在了桌上。","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"扬一周前就偷偷往希曼夫人家跑了好几次......金盏花小巷的所有年轻人，几乎都请过希曼夫人帮忙现场作画留作纪念。","id":345},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"由这两个家伙去吧。新生活的开始......我本来也答应过洛里斯的。","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"早晨风很大，吹得人有些恍惚。街上没什么人往来。","id":347},{"type":"dialog","id":348},{"type":"background","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","x":"-125","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"2","id":349},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1125_1#1$1","posfrom":"300,0","posto":"300,0","duration":"2","id":350},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1127_1#1$1","posfrom":"400,0","posto":"400,0","duration":"2","isblock":"true","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"我好像注意到了咖啡馆对面的拐角似乎站着两个人......","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"黑色的面具......上面刻着扭曲的纹样......","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"他们也注意到了我。他们走了过来。","id":354},{"type":"dialog","id":355},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":356},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","posfrom":"400,0","posto":"300,0","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1.5","id":357},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","action":"zoom","poszoom":"0.5,0.5","scale":"1.1","duration":"2","id":358},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","posfrom":"300,0","posto":"200,0","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1.5","id":359},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","action":"zoom","poszoom":"0.5,0.5","scale":"1.1","duration":"2","isblock":"true","id":360},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_spellattack_1","volume":"1","id":361},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":362},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":363},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":364},{"type":"charslot","id":365},{"type":"curtain","id":366},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":367},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":368},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0","keep":"true","id":369},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","id":370},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#2$1","id":371},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":372},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":373},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#2$1","focus":"n","id":374},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"巫王残党......这也能解释为什么“始源之角”中巫王的术式会在你眼中化为具象。","id":375,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"这是你生前和巫王唯一的联系。","id":376,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"......","id":378},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":379},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"真相和洛里斯的猜想有较大出入，你应该是刚好出现在了巫王残党的行动现场......","id":380,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"市政厅并非在庇护一个贵族。作为参与了巫王残党行动的人，芬恩男爵最终的下场也可想而知。","id":381,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"只是在双子女皇执政早期，崔林特尔梅需要让整个案件与巫王及巫王残党无关。","id":382,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"掐断调查的进程，遮掩事情的原貌，尽快结案。最高效的做法。","id":383,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"唔，什么意思？","id":385},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"尤利娅·许勒尔，你的死亡完全是一场意外。","id":387,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b5/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":388},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"......","id":389},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":390},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"我已经知晓了案件的真相。如果回忆这些内容对你造成了负担，请不要再去想它。","id":391,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":392},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"不，执行者先生，我只是在想，如果这条街真的在某个时刻，从“崔林特尔梅”消失，就像那些已不复存在的高塔一样......","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"我是不是再也没有机会，实现和洛里斯的约定？","id":394},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":395},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"从逻辑上讲，你已经......","id":396,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":397},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"执行者先生，你有没完成的约定吗？","id":398},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":399},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"入职公证所以来，除去两次因遗嘱本身描述不明无法执行、两次标的物在爆炸中意外损毁外，没有过失约情况。","id":400,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"呃，我不是说工作。","id":402},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":403},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......“约定”。","id":404,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/37/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":405},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":406},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":407},{"type":"charslot","id":408},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/93/Avg_bg_26_g8_laterano_dwelling.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":409},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":410},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"2","id":411},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":412},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.6","fadetime":"2","id":413},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1120_1#3$1","id":414},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1118_1#1$1","id":415},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.4","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":416},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1120_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":417},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......费迪，你在做什么？","id":418},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1118_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":419},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"画画。","id":420,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_1118_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1120_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":421},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"摸黑画画？","id":422},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1118_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":423},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"并不难。","id":424,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_1118_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1118_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":425},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"只是随便做点什么......你说你需要安静。","id":426,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b8/Avg_avg_npc_1118_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1120_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":427},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"谢谢。","id":428},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1120_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":429},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"你画了什么？","id":430},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1118_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":431},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"拉特兰，夜晚的拉特兰。","id":432,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_1118_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1120_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":433},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"为什么要画夜晚的拉特兰？","id":434},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1118_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":435},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"因为房间没有开灯。","id":436,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_1118_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1120_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":437},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......","id":438},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1118_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":439},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"姐姐，你说话的鼻音在变轻，你没在哭了。","id":440,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/77/Avg_avg_npc_1118_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1118_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":441},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"你说过你会慢慢掌握演奏的方法，我相信你，所有人都说你很有音乐天赋。但通常来说，天赋不应该带来痛苦。","id":442,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_1118_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1120_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":443},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"费迪，我会学会的......这是我必须做到的事情。","id":444},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1120_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":445},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"你要接着画完你的画吗？你似乎遇到了一些困难。","id":446},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1118_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":447},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"嗯......","id":448,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ef/Avg_avg_npc_1118_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1118_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":449},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"已经勾勒好了整体的轮廓，接下来要细化重点。但是......姐姐，拉特兰城进入夜晚的时候，第一个亮灯的地方是哪里？","id":450,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b8/Avg_avg_npc_1118_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1120_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":451},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"......我不知道。","id":452},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1120_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":453},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"要不等我掌握了方法，能正常演奏自己的第一首曲子——不会很久——到时候我可以带你去拉特兰城最高的地方看看。","id":454},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1120_1#12$1","focus":"r","id":455},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"看一看不就知道了？","id":456},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1118_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":457},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"好。","id":458,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_1118_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":459},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":460},{"type":"charslot","id":461},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":462},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0","keep":"true","id":463},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#3$1","id":464},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","id":465},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":466},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":467},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","focus":"n","id":468},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"在我看来，“约定”即是一种契约。","id":469,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b5/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"在定下该契约之时，我的认知能力还不完备，并不清楚她的障碍，以及克服障碍的痛苦意味着什么。","id":470,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b5/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"那是未被定义的混乱。她自己即是她音乐的第一个“受害者”。","id":471,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b5/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":472},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"因此，弄清她变化的全貌，阻止她继续制造混乱，是我应该履行的职责。","id":473,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":474},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"执行者先生，这也是你来到“崔林特尔梅”的理由？","id":475},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"那个人也是萨科塔吗？","id":476},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":477},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"阿尔图罗，女性，身高一百六十八厘米，黑色长直发，左眼眼角有一颗痣，随身携带一把形制特殊的大提琴。","id":478,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":479},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"她比我更早进入这里。你见过她？","id":480,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d3/Avg_avg_1032_excu2_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":481},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","text":"","id":482},{"type":"charslot","id":483},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":484},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":485},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","id":486},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#9$1","id":487},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":488},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","style":"slider","inverse":"true","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":489},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":490},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#9$1","focus":"n","id":491},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"阿尔图罗小姐，你要不别跟着我往前走了。","id":492},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":493},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"为什么？","id":494},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"从街尾的画廊到这里，您刚刚还说，前面就是您的咖啡馆，很快就能改造完全部的共鸣管线。","id":495},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":496},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"您希望我......回避什么？","id":497},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":498},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"......","id":499},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"应该是打伤你的人，虽然他也是萨科塔，但看着很不好说话的样子......","id":500},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":501},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"费德里科？他果然也来到了这里。","id":502},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#12$1","focus":"l","id":503},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"感谢您的细心。如果打伤我的是我这个弟弟，您会在我身上发现几个弹孔。","id":504},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":505},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"你们竟然是姐弟？完全想象不到......","id":506},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":507},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"费德里科他，肯定会追上我的。","id":508},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"意识到自己长久践行的道路存在空白，总不免让人生出困惑。只不过对他而言，疑惑不是涟漪，而是冰面上的裂纹。","id":509},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"在得到解答之前，我们都无法停下。","id":510},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":511},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"那好吧。","id":512},{"type":"dialog","id":513},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":514},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":515},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":516},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":517},{"type":"charslot","id":518},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_dimnlspamb","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"a","id":519},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"1","channel":"a","fadetime":"2","id":520},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":521},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":522},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_mgcdevcstartp","volume":"1","id":523},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":524},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","id":525},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"呼~这是最后一段了......街口的钢琴教室、街尾的画廊，一头一尾，全部的共鸣管线在此交汇。","id":526},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#8$1","id":527},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"尤利娅......","id":528},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1122_1#1$1","id":529},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"阿尔图罗小姐，我知道你想说什么。这可能没有任何作用......那我会想新的办法。","id":530},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"我没法允许自己躲在房间里，惴惴不安地等风暴过去。","id":531},{"type":"dialogue","name":"尤利娅","text":"回声装置已经全部放置好了。接下来，激活共鸣管线。","id":532},{"type":"dialog","id":533},{"type":"charslot","id":534},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.2","channel":"a","fadetime":"1","id":535},{"type":"text","text":"不辨方向，没有天光，一切都是影影绰绰的。“始源之角”仿佛永远陷在蒙蒙的雾气中。","id":536},{"type":"text","text":"但阿尔图罗感知到了共鸣管线的亮起，就像夜色里的，一盏灯。","id":537},{"type":"dialog","id":538},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_magic_4","volume":"1","id":539},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":540},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":541},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":542},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":543},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"1","id":544},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":545},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_signlntrfrnc","volume":"0.8","id":546},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_signalInterference","fade":"true","fadetime":"1.5","layer":"1","id":547},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":548},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":549},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":550},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":551},{"type":"text","text":"以两人为中心，由近及远，周遭的景象逐渐清晰。她真切地看到了尤利娅眼中的一切：一条金盏花摇曳的街道、无数瑰奇的高塔......","id":552},{"type":"text","text":"这里并非一片混沌，而是超越时间与空间而存在的——巨构。","id":553},{"type":"text","text":"与此同时，乐声传入了她的耳朵。","id":554},{"type":"text","text":"那是整个金盏花小巷的乐声，亦是，某个更加盛大的乐章的一部分。那乐章属于，赫尔昏佐伦。","id":555},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#1$1","id":556},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"尤利娅女士，我的琴依然沉默。但我真切地听见了您的心声......它很动人。","id":557},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_245_cello_1#2$1","id":558},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"请允许我向您致意。","id":559},{"type":"dialog","id":560},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"0,-10","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1","isblock":"true","id":561},{"type":"charslot","id":562},{"type":"text","text":"阿尔图罗颔首，向着面前的卡普里尼施礼。","id":563},{"type":"dialog","id":564},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"2","id":565},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":566},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":567},{"type":"image","image":"44_i17","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","y":"-50","fadetime":"0","id":568},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_churchfire","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"b","id":569},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.2","channel":"b","fadetime":"2","id":570},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":571},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":572},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$lab_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_sys_lab_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":573,"musicid":4},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"！！！","id":574},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"原来最平凡的心灵与最强大的心灵，书写在同样的乐谱上。","id":575},{"type":"text","text":"诡异的双翼雕塑在阿尔图罗两侧匍匐，它们以力学难以解释的角度轻易撑起通天的石柱——不，那些石柱本就悬空而立。","id":576},{"type":"text","text":"君王之所，森严而伟丽。","id":577},{"type":"text","text":"阶梯的尽处，男人岿然不动，与王座融为一体。他的面容隐在赤色帷幔荡漾起的层层光影里，无法看清。","id":578},{"type":"text","text":"但那传闻中寄宿着魔鬼的旋角，即是他的名与姓。","id":579},{"type":"dialog","id":580},{"type":"imagetween","yFrom":"-50","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1.2","yScaleFrom":"1.2","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","ease":"OutQuad","duration":"12","block":"false","id":581},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":582},{"type":"cgitem","id":583,"from":"0.4","to":"0","duration":"4"},{"type":"cgitem","image":"cgitem_44_i17","style":"cg","sfrom":"1.4","sto":"1","sduration":"10","pfrom":"0,-120","pto":"0,0","pduration":"10","afrom":"0","ato":"1","aduration":"4","layer":"0","id":584},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":585},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......","id":586},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"我在无数历史与传说的碎片中与您相逢，又在巫妖与许多人的记忆中与您错身。","id":587},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"直到亲眼见到尤利娅还“活着”，我才隐隐预感到，此行真的能见到您本人！","id":588},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"阿尔图罗·吉亚洛，觐见您。","id":589},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿尔图罗","text":"奥托·迪特马尔·古斯塔夫·冯·乌提卡，赫尔昏佐伦......巫王陛下。","id":590},{"type":"dialog","id":591},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"b","fadetime":"2","id":592},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"d","fadetime":"2","id":593},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":594},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":595},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":596},{"type":"charslot","id":597},{"type":"background","id":598},{"type":"image","id":599}],"characters":["薇薇安","薇薇安娜","围观的路人A","围观的路人B","费德里科","尤利娅","阿尔图罗","？？？"]}